	<p>I've seen reference to that too, but it's simply not true...at least not in my experience.  Seems to me that mana regen is the same whether you're poking a critter or just sitting there.<br />
<br />
You do get sitting HP regen while on a horse though...not standing.  Not sure where qhor was coming from on that one.</p>
	
	
	
