	<p>HP regen, 54 barbarian with regrowth and regen III:<br />
<br />
-sitting, no horse: 23 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
-standing, no horse: 20 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
-on horse: 20 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
<br />
HP regen, 54 barbarian with regen III:<br />
<br />
-sitting, no horse: 6 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
-standing, no horse: 5 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
-on horse: 5 HP/tick.<br />
<br />
<br />
as of 4.4.03</p>
	
	
	
	
